OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDeposit return scheme could
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbe axed this month         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scotland's deposit return scheme could 
OL,6, be axed later this month if UK         
OL,7, ministers do not give the go-ahead, the
OL,8, circular economy minister has said.    
OL,10,FLorna Slater said if an exemption from 
OL,11,Fthe Internal Markets Act was not       
OL,12,Fconfirmed then the Scottish government 
OL,13,Fwould have to decide on its future.    
OL,15,FThe BBC understands the UK is unlikely 
OL,16,Fto reach a decision in this timeframe. 
OL,18,FMs Slater told the Scottish Grocers'   
OL,19,FFederation that a lack of response     
OL,20,Fcould render the scheme "unviable".    
